n  <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fhv983e9cllg75eug%3Flanguage%3Dzh-CN%23YHgv6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard>\n  <h2 style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌携程商旅海外本地化探索 — B端视觉体系的构建与实践</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2OTYzMTI1Ng==&amp;mid=2247497295&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=79bbe77bee2b2fcfd22f60b99b4442ff&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/IO_PzRDV_S40TritVjyV3g\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/IO_PzRDV_S40TritVjyV3g</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本报告描述了携程商旅海外本地化探索的全过程，聚焦 Trip.Biz 在全球化框架下实现“国际化标准 + 本地化适配”的设计语言体系建设。通过品牌策略解构、视觉核心资产设计、色彩与字体体系、符号设计及官网多站点落地，形成一套可复用、可扩展且具区域差异化表达的品牌语言，并通过本地化资料库与模块化官网框架实现对不同市场的精准落地与高效传播，提升全球品牌识别度与用户体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968107\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=60b93f0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2Ss9htDxPyXaciaGicVVcn09ibUa8HQL85ZUfE6KBFwicay41wYPfdc2rXMCwGmNdeShyaKXCfG0roHgA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌万字图文：如何从0到1搭建一套自媒体获客AI Agent（建议收藏）</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4MjUzNjc0Mw==&amp;mid=2247491361&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e9e4f1ad59a4154795bead58e409428a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kSTC_PmFuE4sdqwqDlfWOA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kSTC_PmFuE4sdqwqDlfWOA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文介绍一套面向自媒体获客的AI智能体系统，目标是通过构建全流程的智能体部门，实现高效内容创作、精准定位与低成本获客，并提供实际的实施路径、角色分工与落地步骤，帮助用户从0到1搭建可 sustained 的日更短视频产出与数据驱动优化能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968108\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4953703703703705\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=73bde68d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2Ss9htDxPyXaciaGicVVcn09ibLVtAH5yjOxibBgqkv2W1bnvPZoLicF67zO7cdG4l6O23JlMkycKAN4aw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌产品经理对接外部API，4个案例避坑指南！（干货收藏）</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwMjkxNTg1Mg==&amp;mid=2247523866&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=8b74d2612254bde35b80637753b774a7&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LqzygU3nKPX30JYn7-mmIA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LqzygU3nKPX30JYn7-mmIA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文通过四个对接外部API的案例，强调在系统对接中把握沟通、服务质量与数据管理的重要性，指出优秀的API对开发者是向导与优雅服务的体现，而糟糕的对接则容易陷入沟通困难、接口限制、黑盒化风险及数据同步问题等坑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968110\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6853625170998632\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"731\" width=\"731\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bd8378f6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2Ss9htDxPyXaciaGicVVcn09ib39Y1kIBeFWAoeFGh5bVfhiaz5HGeIxicoztA2lII2SdyDwKAAKBkFF8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌ToB服务案例丨从0到1拆解O2O上门服务用户端&amp;技师端全流程设计</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNzQzMzMwOQ==&amp;mid=2247491712&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c0a24bf1c801f6a1acf8a9081e156d73&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/mtUd3c5AIUqzQYjR244J2Q\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/mtUd3c5AIUqzQYjR244J2Q</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文通过设计大侦探的个人案例，系统拆解了O2O上门服务的全流程设计，覆盖从信息架构、交互到UI与UX文案，强调在预算受限的情况下仍可完成用户端核心页面升级，并补充完整的技师端设计参考，提供一个完整的上门服务全链路设计参考框架。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968109\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a556d979&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2Ss9htDxPyXaciaGicVVcn09ibNUlK3ibbubibP0jEqdoUVyYTBPAY00S4QSTckHAhIAOQcB9vnDOhicFSA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌万字详解让大模型写出好代码：上下文窗口的工程化实践</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&amp;mid=2247692063&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c340c3117927abf9d3b58cd4689d8ca5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8tS3EKaLmFiB5VPDH3CudA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8tS3EKaLmFiB5VPDH3CudA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文围绕“大模型在代码生成中的上下文窗口”进行工程化探讨，聚焦上下文窗口的容量、-token机制、以及在实际开发场景中提升代码质量与可维护性的策略，提出从结构化管理、分层检索、动态上下文调整等角度的完整方法论，以帮助专业开发团队在有限上下文中最大化技术信息利用，并实现可扩展的上下文管理框架。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968111\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9027777777777778\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c740ef0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2Ss9htDxPyXaciaGicVVcn09ibacPVk7nNd7b0VibYFyHIcNmzUuBjjCOE6KRWUUwEicQel6gxupVdnUeg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌如何才能从优秀到不可替代</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0NjUwNjc4NA==&amp;mid=2247489067&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=5ee1e84e10dc132f826ab8a09c93f83f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/qwK8ZjgmmKv53utkXgdHGg\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/qwK8ZjgmmKv53utkXgdHGg</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文围绕“从优秀到不可替代”的底层逻辑，提出通过构建价值坐标系、提升跨部门沟通、打造超预期个人价值、规避能力陷阱、建立职场记忆点、进行合理规划与舍得取舍、善用跨界能力、防止被动心理与持续进阶等策略，帮助职场人士以价值交易为核心，持续提升个人竞争力并实现长久成长。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968112\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35648148148148145\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8ca51457&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2Ss9htDxPyXaciaGicVVcn09ibZXj980VrZJhzib22Ah72U3Y8JCkVicbunjWr2dYlls5dmKIRvYRBbP9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌如何快速提升UI设计水平</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTQ2MzE0MA==&amp;mid=2247529492&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=aeac9396ac6ef585f5f27983a968f508&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/IFZ4QWyWGVgHOXPAbhS04A\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/IFZ4QWyWGVgHOXPAbhS04A</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文从临摹、套用和演变三个维度，系统性地探讨初学者及有经验设计师如何快速提升UI设计能力，强调在临摹过程中要拆解规范、手动测量并分析元素关系，通过不断套用高水平设计规范来提升审美与执行力，最终通过大量多风格的临摹与组件化练习积累灵感与技法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968113\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26481481481481484\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=815a3269&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2Ss9htDxPyXaciaGicVVcn09ibx9tUTH1ESeeSohJ23ub1F7Mqd44PrLx8nAU7Ul9aKG3g9nwKLzPBNA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌详解“财务共享中心”：概念、产品架构、各业务处理流程</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2MTg1NTM4NA==&amp;mid=2247509236&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0d2f1378b77a462f27207637be9454c1&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/9o5k9TBdS2GgYfEiabEPyA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/9o5k9TBdS2GgYfEiabEPyA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">财务共享中心（FSSC）通过集中化、标准化和数字化，将分子公司重复性高的财务流程统一处理，达到降本增效与加强管控的目标；实现依托 ERP、云端技术、影像与自动化工具（OCR、RPA、AI）的前后端协同与数据集成，解决跨区域、跨系统的数据孤岛和流程不统一的问题；同时在落地过程中面临变革管理、系统集成和数据治理等挑战，需要持续投入制度、流程、人员与技术的迭代优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968114\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7731481481481481\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a912503&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2Ss9htDxPyXaciaGicVVcn09ibYlrySzLvunht6VbDAogJgVDHlJiaVATuicFia1XfiblOvNaXb5ej6Rp7bA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0em;margin-top: 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-cropsely2=\"65\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 65px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b74e1aca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoloQt5Gibu37EDyzwasmLC9Ld1Z8ia20TCibPO3Vjh9BB9sKKsPwq4k26g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  </h2>\n  <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:n